# Use <C-v> to insert special keys such as '\t' and '\r'
<C-v><Tab>   inserts '\t'
<C-v><C-i>   also inserts '\t'
<C-v><C-m>   inserts '\r' (carriage return)
<C-v><C-j>   inserts '\n'

# To find additional documentation on special keys
:help ins-special-keys

# To list a searchable table of available mappings
:help digraph-table

# To view current mappings
:digraphs


# Use <C-k> followed by digraph shortcut to insert symbol

symbol  digraph  description
------  -------  -----------
•       oo       bullet
◆       Db       diamond bullet
·       ~.       middle dot
ϴ       '%       Greek theta
Δ       D*       Greek delta
£       Pd       British pound symbol
©       Co       copyright symbol
®       Rg       registered trademark symbol
™       TM       trade mark sign
€       Eu       euro symbol
‐       -1       hyphen
–       -N       en-dash
—       -M       em-dash

§       SE       section sign
¶       pp       pilcrow sign
¬       NO       logical not
∪       )U       union
∩       (U       intersection
∑       +Z       sum
Π       *P       product
«       <<       left-pointing double angle quotation mark
»       >>       right-pointing double angle quotation mark
±       +-       plus-minus sign
℅       co       care of
µ       My       micro sign
°       DG       degree sign
℃       oC       degree celsius
℉       oF       degree fahrenheit
“       "6       left double quotation mark
”       "9       right double quotation mark

½       14       fraction one quarter
⅓       13       fraction one third
½       12       fraction one half
⅔       23       fraction two thirds
¾       34       fraction three quarters

